snippet.title: Super Smash Bros. Clash (DS) Rebirth Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a trailer or the next release of Super Smash Bros. Clash, a homebrew SSB for the Nintendo DS, which is codenamed "Rebirth". I slapped it together without much video editing, so excuse the looping music and other things, just watch the gameplay.

SSBC Blog (Subscribe for weekly updates!):
http://screwattack.com/blogs/Super-Smash-Bros-Clash/Super-Smash-Bros-Clash-DS-First-Information

How to play SSBC:
http://screwattack.com/blogs/Super-Smash-Bros-Clash/How-to-Play-SSBC

SSBC Screwattack Tease:
